sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant A as Agent
  participant M as MCP Server
  participant E as Diagram Engine
  participant F as Frontend Editor

  U->>A: Describe architecture
  A->>M: create_component_diagram
  M->>E: validate spec
  E-->>M: validation result
  M->>E: auto layout and render SVG
  E-->>M: DiagramSpec plus SVG
  M-->>A: diagram result
  A-->>F: show generated diagram
  U->>F: drag node
  F->>M: move_node
  M->>E: reroute and render SVG
  E-->>M: updated SVG
  M-->>F: updated diagram
